error[E0277]: (calimero)> `Plain` cannot be stored in replicated state — it is not a CRDT
  --> tests/macros/error_non_mergeable_field.rs:16:1
   |
16 | #[app::state]
   | ^^^^^^^^^^^^^ this type has no merge semantics
